{"tid":1031263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇椰子巴打當年出到黎參選粒聲唔出","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T06:53:35.000Z","uid":37528,"like":48,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd5904988100f32e3e47ae195a5d785e1e9e6ec","tid":1031263,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"椰子巴氣弱柔絲，含羞答答<br />\n差d搽埋水粉，咬埋唇<br />\n好似做陳國強背後既女人咁<br />\n之後番到黎到高登連登又串柒柒，好似唔記得曬當年自己出黎咁柒咁<br />\n仲有成日想玩自嘲，但係自嘲果d又全部係事實黎。自己面對左自己未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實只係想講，毒撚切忌有自信，安安份份做番看更咪算囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthank you for the final proof"},{"pid":"c97d2ad281b4fc982fdb14cd632f5139d77ca08d","tid":1031263,"uid":37528,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"三、本土派間不能再互相攻擊<br />\n本土派彼此之間絕不可再以文革批鬥手段互相攻擊，以免中了中共以人民鬥人民分化瓦解抗爭力量的毒計。「團結就是力量」，我們面對中共國家機器的壓倒性優勢，更應盡可能爭取所有可以合作的力量支持我們。我們不應再浪費時間在無意義的爭論中互相內耗殆盡，我們應將注意力放回值得關注的議題上。我們應優先處理一些力所能及的身邊事務，暫停討論一些仍停留係空中樓閣的長遠大計。<br />\n本土派現時眾人士氣低迷，我們更應儘快取得一場勝利來重振抗爭士氣。我們應由小事入手，積少成多、聚沙成塔，集小勝為大勝。我們不應拘泥於教條主義，我們要審視現實環境和自身條件的考量去採取合適的行動。遊行、集會可以有效的向外界展示力量和團結，從而爭取外界支持。<br />\n前路縱使茫茫，但我們絕不能就此放棄希望；若然我們就此放棄的話，比賽便等於已經完結了。大敵當前，香港期盼每一個人都恪盡其責；因為，世上只有我們係香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢篇野好似當年出自椰子巴手，睇黎係用黎呃like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係轉左會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ad3ba8c4767fc8f8a8f9a89c9eac0e25bf1bff","tid":1031263,"uid":4493,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n行得本土出真樣真名已經慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢都幾大犧牲企出嚟 但係都係鳩做 近呢一兩年就消極憤世嫉俗自暴自棄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578b1b72d104e06a9820e3c9e68354d2f1f4767e","tid":1031263,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"唔係返左去做保安咩"},{"pid":"aa41735e225a1c2764ccb269f11ceeeadb89a500","tid":1031263,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"配金金選立法會先得300幾票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03630d46966e87be3b1b16c4ca5680e28a92485","tid":1031263,"uid":9564,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:26:20.000Z","msg":"2016年8月，正義行動梁金成與陳國強、邱文勁推出立法會新界東選舉競選網站宣傳參選理念。但選舉管理委員會褫奪陳國強的參選資格，只確認梁金成、邱文勁參選，所以該參選名單只有梁金成、邱文勁。<span style=\"color: red;\">最終，該名單取得305票，得票率為0.05%，是該屆選舉中全港得票最低的地區直選侯選人。</span><br />\n唔死都冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4fb61ec809f9ba99e90c74dd139478efce3e53","tid":1031263,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"去邊"},{"pid":"c9a2e7135c17389122eec2f31f280dd13c3f0b5a","tid":1031263,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:04:40.000Z","msg":"當年篇文寫到咁冠冕堂皇，遲啲變咖哩飯二號？"},{"pid":"6e58bf234c63945c5cccda01aba485c26121f876","tid":1031263,"uid":35430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:30:46.000Z","msg":"其實我到依家都唔知邊個係椰子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽過有出黎參選但唔知邊個係椰子<br />\n剩係覺得由正正常常變左個怨婦同班五毛癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b32b2fee2645fc312084a5a0af538729b16715","tid":1031263,"uid":60545,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:47:34.000Z","msg":"人地全面追撃緊關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本土主義？港獨？唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢而家同波台狗 五毛差唔多"},{"pid":"ef3730b27972c506c9124f33d6da6535371cefec","tid":1031263,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T19:49:58.000Z","msg":"圖呢？無圖點笑呀"},{"pid":"62db1cac8b77619e0deb1d0ad51ce4b3db3c81f1","tid":1031263,"uid":66784,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T22:31:22.000Z","msg":"人地而家全面支持韓國瑜兩岸一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aac7eb065b102ab98aff488742b815da2ac4c2f","tid":1031263,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7dU5TW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7dU5TW.png&h=074ee6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自稱本土派但屌鳩同路人嘅邱文勁<br />\n圖source:佢privacy set公開嘅Facebook ac<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arr0g0D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Farr0g0D.png&h=b39f5ced&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HM9Umsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHM9Umsk.png&h=40bd151a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLyBzNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLyBzNn.png&h=b08dda7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3uw77t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3uw77t.png&h=1a04506b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRZpJFV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRZpJFV.png&h=a9a29bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0kDN7C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0kDN7C.png&h=4562c55a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baqTB0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaqTB0Z.png&h=91e